<br>
One reason is the Mend button is down for 6 minutes. That means that the pause time would have to equal 6 minutes. The most you can do in one pause is....not that much, so you would have to have multiple pause statements. <br>
<br>
So you are thinking that this is not such a big deal. Except for the fact that while you are paused you cannot send text messages. <br>
<br>
The next reason is that 6 minutes is a long time in EQ. The healer will never remember correctly if mend is up or not.<br>
<br>
I have 2 hot buttons.<br>
<br>
/g Mend is up, save your mana<br>
/g Mend is down, heal when necessary<br>
<br>
About the time I lose one bubble I hit the appropriate button.  <p>Kurrlee<br>
