<br>
In the case you are grouped with a poor player that has not a clue when to heal, you might want to save your mend until you really need it.<br>
<br>
Or<br>
<br>
When you become victim to the health-meter-lag-bug. Where the healer is not getting health updates in a timely manner. They will see you at full health...then suddenly 1 bubble or dead.<br>
<br>
The end result is typically the same, they will wait until you are under one bubble of health before they even start casting. Unless I have grouped with the healer before and completely trust their skill, I usually get pretty twitchy when my health gets below one bubble. <p>Kurrlee<br>
